<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2024</copyright><pubDate> Fri, 22 Mar 2024 17:47:41 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Apple Silicon has a hardware-level exploit that could leak private data]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一组大学安全研究人员在<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/macbook-air-m3-review-2024-13-15-inch-140053162.html">Apple Silicon Mac</a>中发现了芯片级漏洞。该组织<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://gofetch.fail/files/gofetch.pdf" data-original-link="https://gofetch.fail/files/gofetch.pdf">表示，</a>该缺陷可以绕过计算机的加密并访问其安全密钥，从而将 Mac 的私人数据暴露给黑客。一线希望是，该漏洞将要求您绕过<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-gatekeeper-privacy-macos-security-104715012.html">Apple 的 Gatekeeper 保护</a>，安装恶意应用程序，然后让该软件运行长达 10 个小时（以及许多其他复杂的条件），这会降低您遇到问题的可能性担心现实世界中的威胁。</p><p>该漏洞源自 Apple M 系列芯片的一部分，称为数据内存相关预取器 (DMP)。 DMP 通过抢占式缓存数据来提高处理器的效率。 DMP 将数据模式视为方向，使用它们来猜测接下来需要访问哪些信息。这减少了周转时间，并有助于引发诸如“非常快”之类的反应，这通常<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-m1-upscaled-133046858.html">用来形容 Apple Silicon</a> 。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>研究人员发现攻击者可以使用 DMP 绕过加密。研究人员写道：“通过新的逆向工程，我们发现 DMP 可能代表任何程序激活，并尝试取消引用任何带入缓存的类似于指针的数据。” （“指针”是指示在何处查找特定数据的地址或方向。）“这种行为使大量程序数据面临风险。”</p><p>该组织写道：“本文表明，DMP 带来的安全威胁比之前想象的要严重得多，并展示了首次使用 Apple m 系列 DMP 对安全关键软件进行端到端攻击。”</p><p>研究人员将这次攻击命名为 GoFetch，他们创建了一个应用程序，可以访问 Mac 的安全数据，甚至无需 root 访问权限。 <em>Ars Technica</em>安全编辑 Dan Goodin <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://arstechnica.com/security/2024/03/hackers-can-extract-secret-encryption-keys-from-apples-mac-chips/" data-original-link="https://arstechnica.com/security/2024/03/hackers-can-extract-secret-encryption-keys-from-apples-mac-chips/">解释说</a>：“M 系列芯片分为所谓的集群。例如，M1 有两个集群：一个包含四个效率核心，另一个包含四个性能核心。只要 GoFetch 应用程序和目标加密应用程序在同一性能集群上运行 - 即使在该集群内的不同核心上 - GoFetch 也可以挖掘足够的秘密来泄露秘密密钥。”</p><p>这些细节技术性很强，但如果您想进一步深入了解<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://arstechnica.com/security/2024/03/hackers-can-extract-secret-encryption-keys-from-apples-mac-chips/" data-original-link="https://arstechnica.com/security/2024/03/hackers-can-extract-secret-encryption-keys-from-apples-mac-chips/"><em>，Ars Technica 的文章</em></a>值得一读。</p><p>但对于外行来说，有两个关键要点：苹果无法通过软件更新来修复现有芯片（至少不会显着降低<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-m3-chips-pro-max-003004080.html">Apple Silicon 的商标性能</a>），并且只要你打开苹果的 Gatekeeper（默认） ，您一开始就不太可能安装恶意应用程序。 Gatekeeper 仅允许来自 Mac App Store 的应用程序以及来自 Apple 注册开发人员的非 App Store 安装。 （在 macOS 安全设置中手动批准来自未注册开发者的应用程序时，您可能需要格外小心。）如果您不在这些限制之外安装恶意应用程序，那么影响您的 M 系列 Mac 的可能性似乎很低。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-silicon-has-a-hardware-level-exploit-that-c​​ould-leak-private-data-174741269.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-silicon-has-a-hardware-level-exploit-that-could-leak-private-data-174741269.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8e6205e9-cfd9-466a-a661-b84e896ccb8c</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Will Shanklin]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 22 Mar 2024 17:47:42 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1711129663</ingested><modified> 2024-03-22T17:47:55+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Computing]]></category><category><![CDATA[Computer Science]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="806" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-03%2F079d1e70-e871-11ee-bffb-07ced50bdd29&amp;resize=1400%2C806&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=b065bceb612fc2dca3697738a2c5af6cbc1eb71a" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="806" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-03%2F079d1e70-e871-11ee-bffb-07ced50bdd29&amp;resize=1400%2C806&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=ec1ac43cc12e7f2ede18802e08feade61b1256ed" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Devindra Hardawar / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Photo of two Apple MacBook Airs, sitting one in front of the other on an outdoor table or desk.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Apple M3 MacBook Air]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The second Final Fantasy XVI DLC, The Rising Tide, will arrive on April 18]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-review-a-whole-new-world-140018063.html"><em><ins>最终幻想7重生</ins></em></a><em>&nbsp;</em>该游戏仅在几周前发布，但该系列的粉丝们无需等待很长时间就能玩到另一款最新游戏的新内容。 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-xvi-review-ps5-140058789.html"><em><ins>《最终幻想 XVI》</ins></em></a>的第二个付费扩展<em>包《涨潮》</em>将于 4 月 18 日上市。</p><p>发行日期在<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aR6arpX94Bg" data-original-link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aR6arpX94Bg">PAX East 小组</a>上<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://twitter.com/wario64/status/1771213817155862711" data-original-link="https://twitter.com/wario64/status/1771213817155862711"><ins>公布</ins></a>，并宣布<em>《The Rising Tide》的</em>售价为 20 美元。然而，如果您还没有购买之前的付费 DLC《 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-first-final-fantasy-xvi-dlc-echoes-of-the-fallen-is-out-now-043119823.html"><em><ins>堕落者的回声》</ins></em></a> ，您可以通过折扣扩展通行证以 25 美元的价格抢购这两个 DLC。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p><em>在《涨潮》中</em>，克莱夫和他的同伴将前往密西迪亚的隐秘之地。当他们寻找利维坦（一种失落已久的水之圣象）的统治者时，他们将“揭开一个被遗忘的民族的悲惨历史”。与<em>《堕落者的回声》</em>一样，该动作发生在主游戏结束之前。 </p><div id="792767d80fde44e8b1ec444a1d8344d9"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jfl3KgFrAQc?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div></div><p>正如标题和描述所暗示的那样，你将使用一系列基于水的攻击，包括“吐海蛇”。 <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/03/22/final-fantasy-xvis-the-rising-tide-dlc-unleashes-leviathan-on-april-18/" data-original-link="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/03/22/final-fantasy-xvis-the-rising-tide-dlc-unleashes-leviathan-on-april-18/">PlayStation 博客</a>还调侃克莱夫将在他的旅程中找到另一种力量。与此同时，预告片展示了与利维坦的战斗，这场战斗发生在湖面上。</p><p>那些击败了<em>《涨潮》</em>和主游戏的玩家将能够进入一种名为 Kairos Gate 的新游戏终局模式。你将在 20 个难度不断增加的关卡中战斗，击倒一波又一波的敌人。通过这个模式你可以为克莱夫赚取新的材料和武器。</p><p>除此之外，Square Enix 将于 4 月 18 日发布<em>《最终幻想 XVI》</em>的免费更新，其中包括一系列生活质量升级。一方面，你可以通过“快速完成”选项立即返回给你任务的 NPC。技能集功能可让您保存最多五个专长和能力负载。在可访问性的积极更新中，您将能够根据需要重新映射控件。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-second-final-fantasy-xvi-dlc-the-rising-tide-will-arrive-on-april-18-174232733.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-second-final-fantasy-xvi-dlc-the-rising-tide-will-arrive-on-april-18-174232733.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 04b2eb60-29ba-4be7-bd1d-1f94895169d3 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Kris Holt]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 22 Mar 2024 17:42:32 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1711129352</ingested><modified> 2024-03-22T17:42:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-03%2F25173de0-e872-11ee-953f-2146a497e9d8&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=f988d7362e17916f51b4475cbc23044846847824" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-03%2F25173de0-e872-11ee-953f-2146a497e9d8&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=ccdaa7d471379c61078797d6cb1eef0037f4021d" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Square Enix]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Clive runs through a flooded landscape in Final Fantasy XVI.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Clive runs through a flooded landscape in Final Fantasy XVI.]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Joni Mitchell joins Neil Young and returns to Spotify]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>标志性歌手乔尼·米切尔 (Joni Mitchell) <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/mar/22/joni-mitchell-follows-neil-young-in-returning-her-music-to-spotify"><ins>在离开 Spotify 两年多后，将她的音乐重新放回到 Spotify 上</ins></a>，以抗议该平台传播有关 COVID-19 疫苗的错误信息，这些信息通常由<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/joe-rogan-balance-things-out-spotify-disinformation-measures-085039569.html"><ins>强壮的播客坏男孩乔·罗根 (Joe Rogan)</ins></a>传播。这发生在抗议者同伴<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/neil-young-is-returning-to-spotify-after-boycotting-it-over-joe-rogans-vaccine-comments-071217691.html"><ins>尼尔·杨重新加入流媒体服务</ins></a>一周后。</p><p>米切尔没有就她的音乐重返 Spotify 发表任何评论。早在 2022 年，米切尔就在一份声明中写道，“不负责任的人正在散布谎言，导致人们丧生。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://pitchfork.com/news/joni-mitchell-returns-music-to-spotify-after-two-year-protest/">在<em><ins>Pitchfork</ins></em><ins>发表的“</ins></a>新冠疫苗问题”上，我与 Neil Young 以及全球科学界和医学界站在一起<em>。</em></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Young 重返 Spotify，理由是 Joe Rogan 的播客<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/joe-rogan-reportedly-nabs-another-250-million-from-spotify-to-share-his-big-brained-ideas-192007040.html"><ins>不再是该平台独有的</ins></a>，因为它现在出现在 YouTube、Apple Podcasts 和 Amazon Music 上。他在一篇博文中写道：“我的决定是在苹果和亚马逊音乐服务商开始提供我在 Spotify 所反对的虚假信息播客功能之际做出的。”该博文在发表后可能已被删除。这位歌手还指出，如果他从上述每个平台上撤下自己的音乐，歌迷将无处可去。</p><p>除了显而易见的原因之外，杨和米切尔在打击医疗错误信息方面也有着个人利益。两位音乐家都是脊髓灰质炎的受害者，这种疾病<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/history-disease-outbreaks-vaccine-timeline/polio"><ins>在北美因疫苗而被消灭</ins></a>。</p><p>乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）在过去几年中经历了职业生涯的复兴。 2015 年动脉瘤导致她无法表演后，她于 2022 年再次开始现场演奏。这位歌手甚至在今年的格莱美颁奖典礼上表演。至于 Rogan，他最近与 Spotify 签署了一项价值 2.5 亿美元的新协议，以继续他的各种播客业务。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/joni-mitchell-joins-neil-young-and-returns-to-spotify-170655527.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/joni-mitchell-joins-neil-young-and-returns-to-spotify-170655527.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5cce9ead-b97b-424a-9db1-5cc54f9bf8ca</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawrence Bonk]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 22 Mar 2024 17:06:56 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1711127217</ingested><modified> 2024-03-22T17:07:06+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2Fbb255e80-c445-11ee-bed7-29d54cf8e36c&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=6f4047700194cae31318b4bcffe126371b3fcc26" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2Fbb255e80-c445-11ee-bed7-29d54cf8e36c&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=ecc7084a9804971d2acfe9a3ffde93613fa59424" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Kevin Mazur via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA - FEBRUARY 04: Joni Mitchell performs onstage during the 66th GRAMMY Awards at Crypto.com Arena on February 04, 2024 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for The Recording Academy)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[66th GRAMMY Awards - Show]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Activision Blizzard’s ex-CEO Bobby Kotick reportedly wants to buy TikTok]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>去年年底辞职的动视暴雪前首席执行官鲍比·科蒂克(Bobby Kotick)显然对收购 TikTok 感兴趣，因为<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/joe-biden-says-he-would-sign-bill-that-would-force-a-sale-or-ban-of-tiktok-232221156.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/joe-biden-says-he-would-sign-bill-that-would-force-a-sale-or-ban-of-tiktok-232221156.html">美国的一项新法案威胁要禁止该应用程序</a>或强制出售该应用程序。据<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy53c2ouY29tL3RlY2gvd2h5LXRoZS1uZXctZWZmb3J0LXRvLWJhbi10aWt0b2stY2F1Z2h0LWZpcmUtd2l0aC1sYXdtYWtlcnMtN2NkM2Y5ODA_c3Q9am5qdzlocXRyYjhtZmN0IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4NWNhMmYyZi0xYTRiLTQxMjYtYjIwNS0zM2FmZjI2YWVmNDkifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcKp66oz0BjnxyD0uFvyo7cruBAD0HyhP4j1_e9QEOgV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fwhy-the-new-effort-to-ban-tiktok-caught-fire-with-lawmakers-7cd3f980%3Fst%3Djnjw9hqtrb8mfct" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.wsj.com/tech/why-the-new-effort-to-ban-tiktok-caught-fire-with-lawmakers-7cd3f980?st=jnjw9hqtrb8mfct"><em>《华尔街日报》</em></a>报道，科蒂克在上周的一次会议晚宴上向 OpenAI 首席执行官 Sam Altman 和其他与他坐在一起的人提到了合作进行此类收购的想法，并向字节跳动执行董事长张一鸣提出了这一想法。 <em>《华尔街日报》</em>指出，如果 TikTok 被出售，其价格可能高达数千亿美元。</p><p>科蒂克领导动视暴雪超过 30 年，但离开时并没有留下什么好印象。 <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/activision-blizzard-sec-settlement-workplace-complaints-whistleblower-153534419.html"><ins>近年来，该公司面临多起诉讼</ins></a>，其中包括去年 12 月与<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://calcivilrights.ca.gov/2023/12/15/civil-rights-department-announces-settlement-agreement-to-resolve-employment-discrimination-and-equal-pay-lawsuit-against-activision-blizzard/"><ins>加州民权部</ins></a>就涉嫌<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/activision-blizzard-will-pay-54-million-to-settle-californias-gender-discrimination-lawsuit-101149166.html"><ins>薪酬歧视达成</ins></a>和解的一起诉讼。 2021年， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/activision-blizzard-call-for-bobby-kotick-resignation-194953539.html"><ins>动视暴雪员工举行罢工</ins></a>，要求科蒂克辞职，但没有发生。科蒂克最终继续担任动视暴雪的负责人<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bobby-kotick-will-remain-activision-blizzard-ceo-until-the-end-of-2023-184419538.html"><ins>，直到 2023 年微软完成收购</ins></a>。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>科蒂克据称对 TikTok 感兴趣之际，立法者上周推出了《保护美国人免受外国对手控制应用程序法案》， <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:8;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/biden-tiktok-ban-bill/" data-original-link="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/biden-tiktok-ban-bill/">拜登总统表示</a>，如果该法案获得通过，他将签署该法案。该法案将于周三提交众议院投票，根据该法案，TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:9;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/lawmakers-have-a-new-plan-to-force-bytedance-to-sell-tiktok-220408004.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/lawmakers-have-a-new-plan-to-force-bytedance-to-sell-tiktok-220408004.html">必须在六个月内出售该应用程序</a>。否则，它将被美国应用商店禁止。</p><p>该法案突然势头强劲后，TikTok 一直试图让数百万美国用户团结起来，并于上周发出推送通知<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:10;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-is-encouraging-its-users-to-call-their-representatives-about-attempts-to-ban-the-app-202056111.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-is-encouraging-its-users-to-call-their-representatives-about-attempts-to-ban-the-app-202056111.html">，要求用户致电其代表</a>。众议院投票后，该法案预计将在上周获得能源和商业委员会一致通过后获得批准，然后将进入参议院。尽管立法者对 TikTok 的担忧主要集中在对数据隐私及其与中国的联系的担忧，但<em>《华尔街日报》</em>指出，让 Altman 参与收购可能会让该应用程序有可能被 OpenAI 用于训练其人工智能模型，但这并不完全是事实。听起来也很适合用户。</p><p><strong>更新，美国东部时间 2024 年 3 月 22 日中午 12:59：</strong>本文已更新，以澄清动视暴雪与 CRD 和解的性质，并删除了对前首席执行官鲍比·科蒂克 (Bobby Kotick) 的不相关指控的提及。虽然 CRD 诉讼最初包括对动视暴雪助长性骚扰的指控，但 CRD 一月份提交了一项修正案，撤回了这些指控，并且公开提交的<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://calcivilrights.ca.gov/wp-content/uploads/sites/32/2024/01/2024.01.17-Order-on-Consent-Decree-SIGNED-CONFORMED.pdf"><ins>和解协议</ins></a>指出：“没有任何法院或任何独立调查证实任何指控：或动视暴雪普遍存在的性骚扰； ......或者动视暴雪的董事会，包括其首席执行官罗伯特·科蒂克，在处理任何工作场所不当行为事件方面行为不当。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/activision-blizzards-ex-ceo-bobby-kotick-reportedly-wants-to-buy-tiktok-210826589.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/activision-blizzards-ex-ceo-bobby-kotick-reportedly-wants-to-buy-tiktok-210826589.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 85ca2f2f-1a4b-4126-b205-33aff26aef49 </guid><dc